description: Race like a champion in F100 2016 and get closer to the world's most exciting motorsport. F100 2016 puts you in the cockpit and in the heart of the action with a stunning new graphic engine that recreates real world physics.
feature_description: The most inclusive F100 racing experience ever.:Featuring a naturally authentic purely physics-based handling model with enhancements and additions in over 20 areas.:"http://acme.com/f100/inclusive", The most inclusive experience.:F100 2016 is designed to be player inclusive for both seasoned players and those new to the series.:"http://acme.com/f100/seasoned",Race like a champion.:"With a pure racing focus, whether you are a novice racer playing on a gamepad or an experienced gamer playing with a wheel, the new handling model will allow you to race like a champion.":"http://acme.com/f100/champ",All the thrills of the 2015 Formula One Hundred World Championship.:"The race calendar for 2016 also features a new circuit, with a return to Springfield for the first time in over 20 years.":"http://acme.com/f100/thrills"
